column4: "Property `user` should be a valid IRI to an existing User."
"Property `userGroup` should be a valid IRI to an existing UserGroup."
"Property `expiredAt` should be a valid datetime (`Y-m-d` or `Y-m-d H:i:s`)."
"Property `name` has a min length of 2 characters."
"Property `name` has a max length of 255 characters."
